sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Controller as LikeV1Controller
    participant Facade as LikeFacade
    participant UserService
    participant ProductService
    participant LikeService
    participant DB

    %% 좋아요 등록
    Note over User, DB: POST /api/v1/products/{productId}/likes (좋아요 등록)

    User->>Controller: POST /api/v1/products/{productId}/likes
    Note over Controller: Interceptor — loginId/loginPw 검증 후 userId 주입

    alt 유저 없음 또는 비밀번호 불일치
        Controller-->>User: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Controller->>Facade: like(userId, productId)
    Facade->>ProductService: getProduct(productId)
    ProductService->>DB: SELECT products WHERE id = productId

    alt 상품 없음
        ProductService-->>Facade: CoreException(NOT_FOUND)
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException
        Controller-->>User: 404 Not Found
    end

    Facade->>LikeService: like(userId, productId)
    LikeService->>DB: SELECT likes WHERE user_id = ? AND product_id = ?

    alt 이미 좋아요한 상품
        LikeService-->>Facade: CoreException(CONFLICT)
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException
        Controller-->>User: 409 Conflict
    end

    LikeService->>DB: INSERT likes
    LikeService->>DB: UPDATE products SET like_count = like_count + 1
    LikeService-->>Facade: LikeModel
    Facade-->>Controller: LikeInfo
    Controller-->>User: 201 Created

    %% 좋아요 취소
    Note over User, DB: DELETE /api/v1/products/{productId}/likes (좋아요 취소)

    User->>Controller: DELETE /api/v1/products/{productId}/likes
    Note over Controller: Interceptor — loginId/loginPw 검증 후 userId 주입

    alt 유저 없음 또는 비밀번호 불일치
        Controller-->>User: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Controller->>Facade: unlike(userId, productId)
    Facade->>LikeService: unlike(userId, productId)
    LikeService->>DB: SELECT likes WHERE user_id = ? AND product_id = ?

    alt 좋아요하지 않은 상품
        LikeService-->>Facade: CoreException(NOT_FOUND)
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException
        Controller-->>User: 404 Not Found
    end

    LikeService->>DB: DELETE likes WHERE user_id = ? AND product_id = ?
    LikeService->>DB: UPDATE products SET like_count = like_count - 1
    LikeService-->>Facade: void
    Facade-->>Controller: void
    Controller-->>User: 200 OK

    %% 내가 좋아요한 상품 목록
    Note over User, DB: GET /api/v1/users/{userId}/likes (좋아요 목록 조회)

    User->>Controller: GET /api/v1/users/{userId}/likes
    Note over Controller: Interceptor — loginId/loginPw 검증 후 userId 주입

    alt 유저 없음 또는 비밀번호 불일치
        Controller-->>User: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Controller->>Facade: getMyLikes(requestUserId, pathUserId)
    alt 헤더 userId ≠ path userId
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException(FORBIDDEN)
        Controller-->>User: 403 Forbidden
    end

    Facade->>LikeService: getLikedProducts(userId)
    LikeService->>DB: SELECT products JOIN likes WHERE likes.user_id = ?
    LikeService-->>Facade: List~ProductModel~
    Facade-->>Controller: List~ProductInfo~
    Controller-->>User: 200 OK ApiResponse(List~ProductResponse~)
